<div class='documentTop'><div>
  
  
    <h1>Guidelines for election observers</h1>
  
  </div></div>
  

  <div class="documentBody" id="Tekstinnhold">   
  <div>
    <p>The Ministry of Local Government and Regional Development has drawn up guidelines for election observation in Norway. The brochure contains both Norwegian and English text. It provides information about the procedure for applying for accreditation, what can be observed during elections, and the “Code of conduct for observers”. </p>
